      {
        title: 'What kind of equipment do I need?',
        description: `You should generally own a DSLR camera or high-quality equivalent that shoots RAW (for photos). A lot of content creators also edit their photos on-the-go either on their computer or phone. You don't need to bring external lights or tools unless you want to.`,
